[22/04/2018 11:07:48] <font color="#0000ff">es tan maravilloso,</font>
[22/04/2018 11:07:53] <font color="#0000ff">el amor del Señor es tan</font>
[22/04/2018 11:07:53] <font color="#0000ff">maravilloso,</font>
[22/04/2018 11:07:59] <font color="#0000ff">el amor del Señor es tan</font>
[22/04/2018 11:07:59] <font color="#0000ff">maravilloso, maravilloso, amor.</font>
